{"tid":1817483,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[I am from Hong Kong] 逾萬遊客每日湧入奧地利「世界最美小鎮」　當地居民：醒來發現房間內有中國遊客","createTime":"2020-01-09T06:31:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-09T06:31:59.000Z","uid":167032,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5917f540a8e1e6e2b1b85e575d17ea5973ab003b","tid":1817483,"uid":167032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T06:31:27.000Z","msg":"被聯合國教科文組織納入世界文化遺產，並譽為「世界最美小鎮」的奧地利小鎮哈爾施塔特 (Hallstatt)，年前起成亞洲旅客的熱門旅遊景點，至今居民仍大受困擾。近日，哈爾施塔特鎮長 Alexander Scheutz 再次開腔懇求遊客不要湧進小鎮，另有當地居民表示，有天睡醒曾發現房間內出現一些中國遊客。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d8569c13f455dcdfa72cae62615ef1952e4a201","tid":1817483,"uid":163704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T06:31:59.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n[全港最大的Fact Check平台-非食店篇]集合超過400間各地區各行業的良心店<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1817378\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1817378</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}